{
  "stem": "10181.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We decided that he-- as we were not his children, there was two possibilities he was going to try and do something for us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was two-- two ways.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One way, there were also deferments where you paid money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One famous one-- which I really had forgotten about, but somebody reminded me of it recently-- was there was a German Jew living in Holland called Friedrich Weinreb who was negotiating with the Germans for money to get so and so many people off transports and kept in Holland.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, of course, it's very controversial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's a very controversial person, and people said he sold, you know, he sold the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he made money out of it, and he was saved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyway, at the time, there was called a Weinreb list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He could have been put on there because my uncle had money outside, you know, with-- with friends, but then he decided he didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He wasn't that happy with Weinreb, and-- and I think he knew him vaguely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he hit upon the idea, we had these Red Cross letters, those which we had gotten.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he went and said, look.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Those two children are actually English citizens, because their mother is living in England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she's probably English by now, and-- and they are English citizens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this actually-- I don't know whether they bought the whole story, but the fact-- there was proof that she was living in England.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was no question about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had some sort of deferment because of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His deferment from being a-- a war veteran lasted for about six weeks or eight weeks, and there was nothing else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he one day was called to a transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
